data.description: Step into the heart of Melrose's prime location and discover the charm of this colonial-style haven on a generous 2.32-acre lot. Enveloped in warmth, this home invites you to create lasting family memories on its private parcel. Nestled on this lot, it's not just a house; it's a space where comfort, privacy, and tranquility seamlessly converge. Welcome to making it your own inviting home in Melrose.
